text: And by that I mean I am following ~20 people and ~80 accounts like “daily YOONGI as a cat” “Daily DILF Seokjin” and “Hourly Namjoon Thighs”. https://t.co/QI56klflDa
Trying to remind myself that “no act of kindness is ever wasted” so I don’t feel like March 2022’s biggest clown.
I’m basically getting close to DAILY therapy at this point and like holy fuck I’d be so screwed if my mother isn’t lowkey rich because these copays 😬.

I’m deactivating & taking a break & making an account with a very small list of people I follow.

This is meant to be an escape, especially during a very very shit period of my life & I’m sick of seeing drama every day instead of HQ pics of Jungkook’s nipples from PTD Seoul.

I also have to write dot points as homework about how I want the chapter to end. I might end up with some naive predictions like “and things worked out with (person) (person) (person) and BTS announced 4 Melbourne shows but she did say the WISHFUL version.

“Don’t forget you are the author of this book though. Your Dad’s death is obviously a chapter and that’s to be expected, but you get to decide how the chapter ends and whether this last month is a page or two or the big moment. I think something else is the character moment”. https://t.co/DT7jHREScC
All I can hope for now is that people let this last month be just a page of the book, not a whole fucking character defining chapter.
I hope the fact I remembered something important to someone today mattered, because no matter what, I want people I care for to feel loved.

I wish dad would come back tonight but I don’t think he will. He was a man of few words. He came, he said them, and now he’ll leave them with me. So therapy, meds, self care, Bangtan content & trying to fight every time my anxiety wants to spiral it is. I hope I got this ✨.

Going to bed early and deactivating tomorrow - already know how to keep in touch with my close friends who will know to tell me the SECOND Namjoon has a Jungkook like wardrobe malfunction and I finally get some toddies. Buenas Noches, May things finally be starting to heal.

I really hope I didn’t make a mistake today sending some texts and I really hope my dad was right when he told me in my dream that everything worth my friends, career, Mamá, anxiety and move to Melbourne will be OK. He was never wrong. I need him to be right one last time ✨✨✨.

I don’t believe in this stuff but in this moment? I feel like my dad is somewhere out there and had watched me sob and have panic attacks for weeks and was like “that’s it, I’m going to pull her damn head in” and yes, those are the words he’d have used trust me.

Had depression nap & forgot to deactivate pero I’m sobbing but in a good way bc I had a dream I was with my dad😭. I don’t even believe in this usually but I swear he came to tell me everything will be ok in April & that my Mamá doesn’t hate me she just doesn’t know how to help.
I made a big typo in one of the 3 short messages I sent so you can def kill me.
I just made a fool of myself and wish to deactivate MYSELF from existence and not just my socials 🙃.

I’m sick of pretending I’m fine & I’m sick of the stigma of depression and anxiety. I’m sick of the pressure to pretend I’m fine so everyone else is more comfortable. So I’m dedicating my energy to therapy, healing & the small group of friends who make me feel supported & loved. https://t.co/3Oy6RWFM1Z
